Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}誰にも見せなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:47.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}キレイなものはキレイ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:50.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}もう知ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:53.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}誰にも聞かなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:57.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}キレイなものはキレイ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:01.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}もう言ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:05.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}あなたの部屋に歩きながら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:10.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}床に何個も落ちる涙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:15.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}自分の価値もわからないような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:20.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}コドモのままじゃいられないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:25.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}心の穴を埋める何か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:29.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}失うことを恐れないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:34.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}自分のことを癒せるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:38.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}自分だけだと気付いたから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:43.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}サイコロ振って出た数進め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}終わりの見えない道だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:53.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}王座になんて座ってらんねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:58.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}自分で選んだ椅子じゃなきゃダメ
Comment: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:26.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}就算誰都不曾見過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:47.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}美麗的東西就是美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:50.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我早已知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:53.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}就算誰都不曾聽聞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:57.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}美麗的東西就是美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:01.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我早已言說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:05.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}一步步走向你的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:10.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}一滴滴落在地板的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:15.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我不願繼續做那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:20.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}不知自愛的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:25.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我不再害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:29.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}那些填補內心空洞的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:34.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}因為我已經發現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:38.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}人只能自己治癒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:43.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}扔出骰子 按點數向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}就算前路漫漫 看不到頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:53.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}哪怕王座 也不能阻擋我的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:58.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我要坐上 自己選的那張椅子
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,EDJP
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,EDCN
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Title
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.02,Default,sc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}擴張的意識
Comment: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.02,Default,tc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}擴張的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.51,0:24:56.01,Default,sc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}共鳴
Comment: 0,0:24:52.51,0:24:56.01,Default,tc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}共鳴
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,screen,,0,0,0,,screen
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不死在千鈞一髮之際救下了彭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你救了我 不死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,救了你？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不死見證了彭向著嶄新的人生邁出了第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他們知曉了敲門者的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,以及它們下一次襲擊的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,到處都是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒地方跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊 救救我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快過橋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,離開城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,往東邊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙 往東邊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我好害怕 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持住 爸爸會來救我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,蹲下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,往東邊的荒野跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊沒有敲門者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,給傷口消一下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是醫生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也需要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這位是貝涅特教的戈爾長老
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只能緩解他的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,往東邊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還剩多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,22000人 都集中在市中心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,情況不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大家似乎都相信神能救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有兩隻在扎根
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要我們怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,別擠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是教督大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這座教堂有信仰的庇護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一同祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再擠擠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,往裡走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們進去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 沒地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這是神明的選擇 關門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不能關門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,戈爾長老？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,敲門者往這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不然所有人都會被活埋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,往外跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一隻在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要在地底爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持住 馬上來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,還有208隻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人呢 敲門者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,敲門者輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但不死也被削弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不死 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它們讓我捎個話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你想奪回他們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就再來參加下一場遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的異端之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你們會玷汙貝涅特教的聖地 快滾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真想守護聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就收回這種愚蠢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪琦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,記得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,帕羅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,托娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:07:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,裡賈德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,失去的有威洛 谷谷 新 帕羅娜 裡賈德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真的想不起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是還記下來了以免忘掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看來並沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就算看著腦子裡也想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了噴火男有點難搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今後它們還會不斷湧現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一次戰鬥就被奪走了5個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣能堅持下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把他們奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有該做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,還有208隻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我該對這些人說點什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,既然他在這邊很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,去了那邊一定也會幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,去了那邊也會幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這種話我可說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,該死 該死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我沒有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚跟你說過話之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人都從教堂裡出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是你救了他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果死去就能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們為什麼還要活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,活著就是為了尋找答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我突然想到的 只是我個人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,或許還有更好的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你的腿還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喬安 過來 有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,願神明保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是它告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這是敲門者下一次襲擊的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,之後就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易奪來的容器 它們會特意還回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我的話 就會一直躲在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,早知道在城裡搞個鴿子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拉不動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,馬？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是來救我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這匹馬是用你的肉體做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒有獲取的能力 但恢復能力很強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,打算在你需要的時候再給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,給我馬有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,現在重點是敲門者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,必須阻止它們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒工夫跟你鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你是讓我別去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 就這麼衝進去肯定會被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡全是沼澤 行動會受限制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,輕易就會被貫穿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣沒準可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我被封在鐵塊裡的時候敲門者就沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它們無法穿透鐵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但要怎麼還擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,裝火藥的箭傷不到沼澤的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,至少要弄清它們到底藏在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色的 你那個感知敲門者位置的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有 但你要擴大感知範圍才能用那個能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我來教你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我切掉了你的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,猜猜是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可是一點也不痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,集中精神你應該能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,繩子的末尾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看 這有層薄膜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是跟我連著的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,手套和其他地方也有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然也有例外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但你造出來的東西會和你相連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在這層膜連著的東西之外再造其他的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這和你的感知範圍成正比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能在此之外創造大地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡就會完全變成你的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我造了一艘大船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就能感知到船所接觸的 並不屬於我的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,前提是你要跟船相連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,經過後天鍛鍊 你的感知會更加敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,水和泥土的感覺很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,造不出那一整片沼澤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能造出石頭和樹枝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎樣跟沼澤裡的敲門者戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是你抓的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我不喜歡魚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害 你很擅長抓魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣沒準能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,敲門者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快來搶我的容器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看我把你整個挖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡就會完全變成你的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,皮歐蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 馬兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可算找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我把這個帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但我已經打敗它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的記憶都回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,騙子 你騙了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙的情報完全是扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的敲門者不是奪走我容器的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我也被它們騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢 沒準是你瞎編的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,黑先生什麼都沒告訴你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但估計他都心知肚明 習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好像下次會襲擊威歐塞耶市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,別急 我會從烏拉里斯派兵過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,趕不上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,下次戰鬥你又想丟掉多少容器？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一個也不想丟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是叫我什麼都不要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該先去變強 好能保護自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,之後再去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說為了擁有永恒生命的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要眼睜睜看著人們被屠殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要管得這麼寬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那些被你忘掉的傢伙都吵吵著不讓你去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎還有一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是敲門者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我來對付
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,迦白 你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你會幫忙吧 我的左手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把你失去的信用贏回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,迦白 你真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有兩下子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,它們讓我捎個話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一年後 我們要去解救連利爾的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,請你們也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你們不來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就會殺死這隻叛變的敲門者和迦白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,連利爾是大陸上最大的都市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在那裡打起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,少說也會有10萬人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,10萬人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還不夠強大 隨時都有可能會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥何時才會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕永遠不會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就算會結束 也是在所有人都死了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那應該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,應該賭上未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要賭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要賭人們的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不死 只要你沒事 我們隨時都能反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓它們奪走那些為了你賭上性命的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘記他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們制定個計劃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你的任務是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要能造出更大的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,更大的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比如像船那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果辦得到 將有利於對抗敲門者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我會準備你需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要在3個月之內完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,3個月？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這期間你就專注於讓自己變強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,對付敲門者和疏散連利爾市民就都交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,之前有在這建城的打算 就運來了很多物資
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但後來計劃泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這艘船就廢棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面的東西你可以隨便用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 這裡就是你的新基地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼需要就告訴牠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,牠會飛到烏拉里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要先回一趟烏拉里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,之後再回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你也保重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,還有動物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,彭 迦白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你們爭取來的時間我會珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,從今天起就要自己一個人努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了還有你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一起努力吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.62,0:24:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,敲門者發佈了一年後的襲擊預告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.29,0:24:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,彭匆忙趕到了襲擊的目的地 連利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.88,0:24:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,獨自開始修行的不死
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.09,0:24:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在馬戲團遇見了一位不可思議的少女
